This is training for OBSOLETE, NO LONGER ADMINISTERED TEST VERSION. This CD-rom is training for "Computer-based test" (CBT). It is no longer administered and has been completely replaced by "Internet-based test" (iBT) since 2006. There are substantial differences between the contents of these two test formats. If you are looking for TOEFL training CD, this is a WRONG ONE. (25 seeders are losers :).

This torrent has at least one functional test CD for the current iBT test: http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/3714997/TOEFL_iBT_Prep_Material

(I've checked that Barron 1 CD works fine, you can download just that file selectively if your torrent client allows.)
